casebody.data:
IN RE Application of DTE ELECTRIC COMPANY to Increase Rates. Residential Customer Group, Appellant,
v.
Michigan Public Service Commission and Michigan Cable Telecommunications Association, Appellees,
and
DTE Electric Company, Petitioner-Appellee. SC: 159096
COA: 338378 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the October 25, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
